Some buses and trolleybuses will change routes in Kiev over the weekend

01 Nov 2019, 17:20


Some buses and trolleybuses will be changed over the weekend due to the fairs in Kiev.

The press service of KP "Kyivpastrans" reports about it.
"On November 2 bus routes # 6, 49, 61, 87, 95 and trolley buses # 34, 37A will be changed, November 3 - buses # 31," the message reads.
According to the information, food fairs are planned on the streets of Liskivskaya, Marina Tsvetaeva, Jordan, Ambrosia Buchma and Tatarskaya.
As it is noted, from the beginning of the movement until the end (approximately till 18:00) the movement will be organized:

trolleybus № 34 from the street. North, then - Ave. Heroes of Stalingrad - ul. Marshal Tymoshenko - ave. Heroes of Stalingrad - ave. Stepan Bandera;
trolleybus № 37А - from Art. m. "Forest" to the street. Liskivskaya along the current route, then on the route route number 37;
bus number 6 from Darnytska Square to the street. Miloslavskaya Street (without arrival at Liskivskaya St. and Radunska St.);
bus number 61 from hall. Sq. "Troyeshchyna" to the street. Radunskoy (without arrival at Liskivskaya Street);
bus number 49 from the hall. Sq. "Left Bank" to the street. Ambrosia Buchma on the active route, further ave. Pavel Tychyna - Dniprovskaya embankment, further along the operating route;



ZIK


bus number 87 in the direction of ul. Metropolitan Andrey Sheptytsky, from Art. Osokorky m. Ambrosia Buchma on the active route, further ave. Pavel Tychyna str. Bereznyakivska, further along the current route;



ZIK


bus number 95 in the direction of the array Mykola Slobidka, from the hall. Sq. "Left Bank" to the street. Ambrosia Buchma on the active route, further ave. Pavel Tychyna - Dniprovskaya embankment, further along the operating route;



ZIK


bus number 31 from the metro station "Polytechnic Institute" to the street. Otto Schmidt on the existing highway, then - ul. Otto Schmidt - ul. Uphill, further along the current highway.

We will remind, since November 1 in Kiev on seven streets limited speed of movement on roads.

